{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":313333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[25],"categories_output":[{"ID":25,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb%e7%90%90%e7%a2%8e","name":"生活琐碎","term_taxonomy_id":25,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":30}],"tags":[225,291,73],"tags_output":[{"ID":225,"slug":"%e5%8e%a6%e9%97%a8","name":"厦门","term_taxonomy_id":225,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":291,"slug":"%e5%a4%a7%e6%b5%b7","name":"大海","term_taxonomy_id":291,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":73,"slug":"%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb","name":"生活","term_taxonomy_id":73,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":11}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_9ab893fb4eadfb02d5c1b657-1000x657-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomabfbeadfbdcbxjpg.jpg",768,339,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_9ab893fb4eadfb02d5c1b657-1000x657-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomabfbeadfbdcbxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_9ab893fb4eadfb02d5c1b657-1000x657-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomabfbeadfbdcbxjpg.jpg",768,339,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_9ab893fb4eadfb02d5c1b657-1000x657-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomabfbeadfbdcbxjpg.jpg",768,339,false],"date_day":"26","date_month":"11","date_month_e":"November","date_year":"2012","date_weekday":"Monday","title":"那隔海相望的瞬间","excerpt":"有时候，自己坐在大海边，浪花一阵阵阴冷的打到脚上和身上，我忍不住笑自己：现在终于与众不同了，能有机会在小有名气的公司做着喜欢的事，一个人跟曾经所有熟悉的地方和人隔海相望。喜劲的背后也是淡淡的忧伤。平凡...","content":"<p><span>有时候，自己坐在大海边，浪花一阵阵阴冷的打到脚上和身上，我忍不住笑自己：现在终于与众不同了，能有机会在小有名气的公司做着喜欢的事，一个人跟曾经所有熟悉的地方和人隔海相望。喜劲的背后也是淡淡的忧伤。</span></p>\n<p><span>平凡的选择，却也是值得的。</span></p>\n<p><span>都说人总要落叶归根，可是自我的选择，可能让我一辈子不可能落叶归根。</span></p>\n<p><span>年少躁动的心，将有太多太多的可能，猜不到也想不到。</span></p>\n<p><span>悲剧仍然管理着生命，可是我们也不妨抓点题材制造点乐趣，别一张苦脸混了一辈子。久而久之或许能反绑了悲剧的手脚。</span></p>\n<p><span>努力是理所当然的，从站上起跑线开始就该思考的问题。有没有努力自己说的都不算，其实是由周遭的人和事来决定的。</span></p>\n<p><span>地球上只有一个我和你。所有无论如何要好好爱护自己和那些认识的唯一的你，好好完成自己的人生。</span></p>\n<p><span>种种喜怒哀乐，都被赋予了意义。</span></p>\n<p><span>就算隔海相望熟悉和想念的人和物，也让我把一切让大海传递出去。</span></p>\n<p><span>孤独寂寞时，可能海浪的声音，就是熟悉的声音。</span></p>\n","slug":"c9cc0077fc1f0314b52c7ffc","prev":[{"ID":213333,"title":"保守产品建站与智能(自助)模板建站的差异分析","excerpt":"《没位道设计提升进阶探索之保守建站与智能（自助）建站的差异分析》","slug":"093bf3ddf84721c7229ba062","post_date":"2012-11-12 15:58:20","post_date_gmt":"2012-11-12 15:58:20","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b69fc72f99a5cc10aadd3aa-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfcfaccaaddaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b69fc72f99a5cc10aadd3aa-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfcfaccaaddaaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_4b69fc72f99a5cc10aadd3aa-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccombfcfaccaaddaaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":223333,"title":"让我就这样坚持做一个幸运儿","excerpt":"很久没写生活日志了，一直忙于各种事情，在我重生的这天，我重新返回了赛场因为今年感恩节前一天，我的腰痛到不行，穿鞋都很困难，行走都会瘫倒，去医院螺旋CT检查后在22号感恩节这天，得知了让我几乎崩溃的消息，L4...","slug":"2012-i-m-lucky-thanks-my-life","post_date":"2012-11-27 18:27:16","post_date_gmt":"2012-11-27 18:27:16","thumbnail":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_e8c4220b03798164384d9bcd-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdbcdxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_e8c4220b03798164384d9bcd-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdbcdxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/images/c945-com_e8c4220b03798164384d9bcd-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomecbdbcdxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2012-11-26 18:27:16","post_date_gmt":"2012-11-26 18:27:16","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2012-11-26 18:27:16","post_modified_gmt":"2012-11-26 18:27:16","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&amp;p=313333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"},"postID":"c9cc0077fc1f0314b52c7ffc"},"__N_SSG":true}